        "management": "Dose 7mg/kg gentamicin (or 20mg/kg amikacin) IV. Interval based on CrCl: >60 = q24h, 40-60 = q36h, <40 = q48h. Check trough before 2nd dose: target <1 (gentamicin) or <5 (amikacin). Hartford nomogram for monitoring."
