          { "feature": "target_trough_lt_1_2_gentamicin", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Used for synergy (e.g., endocarditis with ampicillin). Check steady-state levels after 3rd dose. Adjust dose to achieve target peaks. Extend interval if trough elevated. Monitor creatinine every 2-3 days."
